(2240, 'TAEqIuF5fkyKT95', 21, '', 'Enemies of Kurdistan - Part 3 - Iraq - Documentary about the oppression of Bashur', 'Link to King of Kurdistan video: <br>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xKzw44fYLf4&amp;t=540s <br> <br>Link to part 1 and 2 of &quot;Enemies of Kurdistan&quot;: <br>Part 2 - Iran: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cFekKKEz_ew&amp;t=4s <br>Part 1 - Syria: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eW7wnfg-DUs&amp;t=1s <br> <br>In this new video serie we will talk about the four countries occupying Kurdistan and their oppression towards the Kurds in history. <br> <br>In the third episode we talk about Bashur which is occupied by Iraq. <br> <br>In this video we talk about: <br>- Basic Information <br>- Sykes Picot agreement <br>- Treaty of Sevres <br>- Treaty of Lausanne <br>- The start of the Barzanis <br>- The Exile of Mustafa Barzani <br>- The relation between Karim Qasim and Barzani <br>- The first Kurdish-Iraqi war <br>- The second Kurdish-Iraqi War <br>- The rise of the Baath party in Iraq <br>- Battle of Mount Handrin <br>- The Arabization Campaign <br>- Saddam Hussein <br>- Al Anfal Campaign <br>- Halabja <br>- Mulazin Muhsin <br>- Kurdish civil War <br>- KDP and PUK <br>- Kurds in Iraq War <br>- The new constitution of Iraq <br>- Capture and execution of Saddam <br>- The referendum 2017 <br>- Iraqi capture of Kirkuk <br> <br>Facebook - For daily news, videos, analysis and much more <br>[a]https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Feverythingaboutkurdistan%2F[/a]  <br> <br>Twitter - For discussions and debates with us: <br>[a]https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAlltomKurdistan[/a] <br> <br>Instagram - For daily updates of Kurdistan-situation: [a]https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Feverythingaboutkurdistan%2F[/a]', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/z_KQ_6aeIY4/maxresdefault.jpg', '', 'z_KQ_6aeIY4', '', '', '', '', '', 1555483308, '2019-04-17 06:41:48', 0, 'Kurdistan,documentary,music,blogg,tourism,song,2017,referendum,independence,nature,army', '00:11:27', 0, 1, 'other', 0, 0, '2019/4', 0