(2539, 'Zs44cEBWzEMZTTs', 21, '', 'Nowruz Celebrated in Lebanon and Kurdistan', 'How Nowruz (Iranian New Year) was celebrated in Lebanon, Kurdistan and beyond on 21st March 2017. Subscribe to Journeyman here: [a]http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fsubscription_center%3Fadd_user%3Djourneymanpictures[/a] <br> <br>Nowruz literally translates as &#039;new day&#039; and is the name for the Iranian New year celebrated by Kurdish people across the globe. The traditional festival of spring starts at the exact moment of the vernal equinox. In Lebanon, members of the Kurdish community celebrated the special event by the waterfront in Beirut. <br> <br>For similar stories, see:  <br>The World of Technology - New Videos Every Tuesday <br>[a]https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLlGSlkijht5gsl9QOHOlVyioS2m8mS-K5[/a] <br>Project Loon is Bringing Internet to the Ends of the Earth <br>[a]https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_rfrgzVrRnw[/a] <br> <br>Like us on Facebook: <br>[a]https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjourneymanpictures[/a] <br>Follow us on Twitter:   <br>[a]https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJourneymanNews[/a] <br>[a]https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJourneymanVOD[/a] <br>Follow us on Instagram: <br>[a]https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fjourneymanpictures[/a] <br>For downloads and more information visit: <br>[a]http%3A%2F%2Fwww.journeyman.tv%2Ffilm%2F7053[/a] <br> <br>N2K – Ref. 7053 <br> <br>Journeyman Pictures is your independent source for the world&#039;s most powerful films, exploring the burning issues of today. We represent stories from the world&#039;s top producers, with brand new content coming in all the time. On our channel you&#039;ll find outstanding and controversial journalism covering any global subject you can imagine wanting to know about.', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/59NWeYZyfBM/maxresdefault.jpg', '', '59NWeYZyfBM', '', '', '', '', '', 1555483308, '2019-04-17 06:41:48', 0, 'Journeyman,Journeyman Pictures,nowruz,iranian new year,persian new year,beirut,kurdish new year,nowruz cel